  Chiau3 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2, chai7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 e5 sou2-chai7 han3-jin5 kau3-hoe7 tui3 choe7-choe7 ko-san-chok8 e5 kiu5-to7-chia2 u7 piau2-si7 jiat8-liat8 e5 hoan-geng5. Ti7 chit tiam2, in u7 tui-sui5 in sou2 thiaN3 e5 bok8-chia2 kou3 Ko Toan-chong Bok8-su e5 bou5-iuN7; i ti7 put-eng-kai si2 e5 si5-chun7 si2--khi3, chit e5 su7 u7 hou7 in tai7-ke chin siong-sim. Ko Sian-siN chiu7-si7 hit ui7 ti7 1886 ni5, chai7 Tai5-oan5 te7-it chhu3 nia2 se2-le2 e5 han3-jin5 (Ko Tiong2) e5 sun. I ui7-tioh8 tui3 ko-san-chok8 ka3 Seng3-keng e5 su7, bat siu7 Jit8-pun2 keng2-chhat e5 khou2-chhou2. Koan-he7 i e5 si2 thang siong-sim e5 kou3-su7, ti7-chia lai5 ki3 chit8 pit kiam2-chhai2 iah8 si7 hap8-gi5. 
  Ti7 poaN3-mi5 au7 iok-liok8 nng7 tiam2 e5 si5, u7 lang5 teh phah bok8-su-koan2 e5 mng5. Hit e5 khoan2-sit sui-si7 chin tiam7-cheng7, iau2-ku2 si7 chin un-khun5. Bok8-su mng7 kong2, ¡§Si7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 ?¡¨ In3 e5 lang5 kong2, ¡§Sian-siN ah, chhiaN2 ka3 goan2 chit8 cham7 Seng3-keng. Goan2 e5 si5-kan chi2-u7 poaN3 tiam2-cheng ku2 na7-tiaN7; in-ui7 goan2 ti7 thiN boe7 kng e5 tai7-seng tioh8 tng2-khi3 kau3 chhu3.¡¨ U7 chit8 tin7 ko-san-chok8 e5 lang5 khia7 ti7 mng5-goa7. Keng2-chhat sui-jian5 giam5-giam5 kim3-chi2 in, m7-chun2 i li7-khui in e5 te7-kai3, iau2-ku2 chiah-e5 lang5 ti7 toa7 am3 i2-au7 u7 liu chhut-lai5, poaN5 soaN ke3 nia2 piaN3 chin kin2, kiaN5 lou7 gou7 tiam2-cheng ku2, bok8-tek si7 ai3 beh chiong Kiu3-chu2 ki5-biau7 e5 siau-sit lai5 hak8-sip8 khah siong5-se3 e5 in-toaN. Bok8-su kui jit8 chin bo5 eng5, bo5 the-si5, chiu7 peh--khi2-lai5, chiong Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 pun hou7 chiah-e5 jiat8-sim tui-kiu5 chin-li2 e5 lang5. I u7 chiong chu7-iu5 e5 he2 tiam2-toh8 ti7 in e5 sim-leng5, ia7 hou7 in bak8-chiu u7 ti3-hui7 sin e5 kng-beng5, chiah chhe in tng2-khi3 (tioh8 koh chit8 pai2 e5 gou7 tiam2-cheng ku2 bo5 hioh-khun3 kiaN5 soaN-lou7). In tioh8 ti7 thiN boe7 kng e5 si5 kau3 chhu3, na7 bo5, kiaN-liau2 keng2-chhat oe7 chai-iaN2 in bo5 ti7-teh. 
  Chit e5 tai7-chi3 m7-si7 chit8 pai2 a2 nng7 pai2, u7 kui2-na7 tin7 bo5 kang7 lang5 e5 ko-san-chok8 pi3-bit8 lai5 siu7 i e5 ka3-si7. Bok8-su sim chun5 lin5-bin2, boe7 thang bo5 ka3-si7 in lai5 pang3 in tng2-khi3; chong2-si7 i chai-iaN2 tai7-chi3 na7 siu7 hoat-kak e5 si5, keng2-chhat un2-tang3 chin siu7-khi3. Ui7-tioh8 ko-san e5 iuN5-kun5 boe7 to5-thoat-tit e5 un7-mia7, hoan5-lo2 chai7 sim, choe7-choe7 mi5 bo5 khun3. In-ui7 Jit8-pun2 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2 koat-i3 beh biat8-choat8 chit e5 goa7-kok chong-kau3, chiu7-si7 tu2-a2-chiah ti7 soaN-te7 tit-tioh8 te7-ki e5. 
  Kau3-be2 keng2-chhat chai-iaN2 chit chan5 su7. In u7 khoaN3-tioh8 kui2 pun2 Seng3-keng, chiu7-si7 bok8-su sou2 pun hou7 ko-san-chok8--e5. Keng2-chhat siu7-khi3, pang3 he2 sio Seng3-keng, iah8 phah hiah-e5 u7 Seng3-keng e5 lang5. Na7-si7 lun7-kau3 bok8-su ne3, i u7 tu2-tioh8 bo5 kiong5-chin7 e5 sim2-mng7, i2-kip8 chan5-jim2 e5 khou2-chhou2. Put-tan3 an2-ni, ti7 cho7-lou7 e5 si5, u7 siu7 bian2-kiong2 lai5 seng5-siu7 chin tang7 e5 ¡§kong-kang.¡¨ In-ui7 siu7-tioh8 hiah chan5-jim2 e5 khoan2-thai7, kho2-lin5 e5 bok8-su cheng-sin5 san3-loan7, chiu7 koe3-sin khi3. 
  Hi-seng-chia2 m7-si7 kan-ta i chit8 lang5 na7-tiaN7. U7 chit8 ui7 ko-san e5 lang5, chiu7-si7 lai5 chhe7 bok8-su kiu5 ka3-si7 e5, iah8 hou7 keng2-chhat phah chin thiam2, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni iah8 koe3-sin khi3. Chong2-si7 tng i iau2-boe7 koe3-khui3 e5 si5, u7 ui5-gian5 hou7 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, kong2 i chin hoaN-hi2, ui7-tioh8 Ki-tok e5 ian5-kou3 lai5 siu7 si2, ia7 i soe3-kiaN2 tioh8 hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3, tioh8 chai-poe5 i, hou7 i chiaN5-cho3 chit8 mia5 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. 
