  Chian3-cheng cheng5, chai7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 A-mi-chok8 u7 khah lim2 chit8 taN2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. Hit ui7 cho3 in e5 leng2-siu3 e5 chheng-lian5 siu7 keng2-chhat phaiN2 khoan2-thai7, lou7-boe2 siu7 tiau3 ka-jip8 Jit8-pun2 kun. Chu7-chai7 ti7 Hiong-kang2 e5 si5, i u7 kap chit8 e5 Sai3-siat-chok8 e5 chheng-lian5 chiap-chhiok; chit ui7 chheng-lian5 si7 tui3 san-te7 (hoan-kai3) e5 sai pak peng5 hia siu7 tiau3 khi3 e5. Chit e5 siong-hoe7 e5 ki-hoe7, kiat-ko2 u7 tit-tioh8 hit ui7 Sai3-siat chheng-lian5 lai5 sin3 Chu2. I ti7-chian3-au7 tng2-lai5 e5 si5, ti7 in e5 tang5-chok8 tiong khai-si2 kang-chok. Chit nng7 ui7 chheng-lian5 piN5-piN5 u7 jip8 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, hian7-si5 choan-kang teh thoan5-to7. 
  Bu2-lun2-chok8 tui3 lan2 e5 thoan5 hok-im u7 piau2-si7 jiat8-liat8 e5 hoan-geng5. Tiam3 ti7 Li2-lang7 e5 thau5-lang5 ka7 Sun Sian-siN kong2 i e5 kiaN2 bat siu7 phian-jip8 Jit8-pun2 e5 kun-tui7, siu7 phai3 loh8-khi3 lam5 Thai3-peng5-iuN5. Jit8-pun2 lang5 ka7 in kong2 in na7 thai5-su hou7 lang5 liah8-khi3 e5 si5 lian5-hap8-kun oe7 thai5-si2 in, soa3 chiah8 in e5 bah. Au7-lai5 i e5 kiaN2 hou7 lang5 liah8-khi3 e5 si5, i put-chi2 gong5-ngiah8, in-ui7 bo5 siu7 lang5 khou2-chhou2, tian-to3 siu7-tioh8 chhin-chhiat e5 thai7-gu7. U7 chit8 ui7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 i-seng ti7-liau5 i e5 siong-jiah, tui3 i hian2-chhut i3-goa7 e5 gau5 khoaN3-kou3. I tng2-lai5 u7 tui3 san-te7 long2-chong2 e5 Bu2-lun2 tong5-pau kong2-khi2 chit e5 tai7-chi3. Tui3 chit ui7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 i-su sou2 hian2-chhut e5 chhin-chhiat u7 cho7-chiaN5 chit8 e5 chin toa7 e5 in3-siong7, chiu7-si7 pi2 lian5-hap8-kun sou2 u7 e5 chian3-lam7 kap eng-cha3-ki koh khah toa7 e5 in3-siong7. Hit ui7 thau5-lang5 kong2, ¡§Goa2 taN chai-iaN2 peh8-bin7 lang5 m7-si7 goan2 e5 tek8-jin5 lah, goa2 chin ai3 goa2 e5 tong5-pau long2-chong2 chiaN5-cho3 Ki-tok-tou5.¡¨ 
  Toa3 ti7 lam5-pou7 hiah-e5 u7 khui3-lat8 e5 Pai5-oan-chok8 kau3 taN iau2 si7 chin oh-tit-thang chiap-chhiok e5. Chong2-si7 kang7-khoan2 e5 ki-hoe7 teh tan2-hau7 lan2 ti7-chia thoan5 hok-im. Ti7 choe3-kun7 choe7-choe7 pai2 e5 chip8-hoe7 tiong, u7 chit8 pai2, hoe7 beh kiat-sok e5 si5, u7 chit8 e5 chin u7 se3-lek8 e5 thau5-lang5 khia7 khi2-lai5 kong2, ¡§Kin-a2-jit8 lan2 thau5 chit8-pai2 thiaN-tioh8 chit e5 ho2 siau-sit. Goa2 si7 lau7-lang5, chong2-si7 chu7 goa2 cho3 gin2-na2 kau3 chit-tiap8 ui5-chi2, goa2 boe7 bat thiaN-tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 siau-sit. Lan2 kin-a2-jit8 sou2 thiaN e5 ki3-jian5 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 su7, goa2 u7 taN2-sng3 beh chiap-lap8 i, goa2 chin ai3 khoaN3 goa2 e5 tong5-pau iah8 long2 chiap-lap8 i.¡¨ 
  Sin-tek e5 han3-jin5 bok8-su kap i e5 kiaN2 ti7 san-te7 e5 sai-peng5 Kap-pan2-san e5 toe7-hng khai-si2 kang-chok. Ti7 chit e5 toe7-hng siang7 te7-it u7 se3-lek8 e5 ko-san-chok8, chiu7-si7 chit8-ui7 siN3 Lim5 e5 i-seng i2-kip8 chit8-ui7 hu7-lu2 kio3-cho3 Li2 Goat8-kiau. Ti7 lian5-siok8 kui2-na7 pai2 e5 chu7-hoe7--nih, in nng7 lang5 in-ui7 tam-tng thong-ek8 e5 koan-he7, sou2-i2 tui3 hok-im chiu7 siN-khi2 heng3-chhu3. Chong2-si7 in nng7 lang5 bat kui2-na7 ni5 ku2 kam2-cheng5 bo5 tu2-ho2. Ti7 lou7-be2 hoe5 e5 chu7-hoe7, u7 chit8 pai2 in nng7 lang5 long2 chhut-sek8, thiaN-tioh8 Ni5-ko-ti2-bo2 e5 kou3-su7 kap Chu2 e5 beng7-leng7 ¡§Lin2 tioh8 teng5-thau5-siN¡¨ hit ku3 oe7. Keh tng2-jit8 thau3-cha2, Li2 Goat8-kiau khi3 hit ui7 i-seng hia, ka7 i kong2, ¡§Lan2 tioh8 lai5 teng5-thau5-siN, tai7-ke koh lai5 teng5 phah-khi2, ke3-khi3 e5 su7 long2 pang3 hou7 boe7 ki3-tit, taN lai5 saN-kap oah8 ti7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 to7-li2.¡¨ Ti7 hit jit8 e5 thiN-kng-cha2, in nng7 lang5 chiu7 ho5-kai2. I2-au7 ke3 boe7 loa7 ku2, hit ui7 i-seng i5-choan2 khi3 Tai5-pak, ti7 san-te7 oe7-seng-kho3 hok8-bu7. Li2 Goat8-kiau iah8 khi3 Tai5-pak, siu7 hun3-lian7 teh beh cho3 choan-jim7 e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2. Hit e5 i-seng choe3-kun7 u7 lai5 chhe7 i, ka7 i kong2, ¡§Goa2 boe7 tit li2-kai2 ti7 li2 e5 sin-chiuN7 sou2 hian2-chhut e5 pian3-chhian, in-ui7 li2 goan5-lai5 koan3-si3 lim chiu2, chiah8 hun, me7 phaiN2 chhui3, siong7-chhiaN2 seng3-te7 iah8 chin oe7 kiaN lang5; m7-ku2 li2 hian7-si5 oan5-choan5 pian3-khoan2 lah.¡¨ I oe7 tit tui3 i kong2-khi2 chit e5 pian3-chhian e5 li2-iu5; in-ui7 i hian7-si5 ¡§ti7 Ki-tok si7 sin chhong3-cho7 e5 lang5,¡¨ phau7 sin e5 jin5-seng-koan. Tai7-ke teh ng3-bang7 chit ui7 u7 leng5-lek8 e5 hu7-lu2 oe7 thang chiaN5-choe3 te7-ji7 e5 Chi-oang2, hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7, thang ti7 sai-hai2-hoaN7 lai5 choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-chok, chhin-chhiuN7 Chi-oang2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 sou2 choe3 e5 chit8-iuN7; in-ui7 i u7 beng5-hian2 e5 kian3-cheng3 ti7-teh, ia7 hit e5 kian3-cheng3 chiu7-si7 eng7 i e5 sit8-te7 keng-giam7 choe3 te7-ki e5. 
  Chai7 Bu7-sia7 e5 sou2-chai7, iah8 u7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 tiong7-iau3 e5 tiong-sim ti7-hia. Bu7-sia7 e5 ui7-ti3 si7 ti7 in e5 hun-pou3 te7-tai3 e5 sai-lam5 kak. Tui3 Bu7-sia7 khoaN3 loh8 ke7 e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7-si7 Pou-li2 ko-goan5, hia u7 han3-jin5 e5 i5-bin5-thoan5 hoan5-eng5 e5 long5-hng5. Hia e5 han3-jin5 kau3-hoe7 e5 Bok8-su Lo5 Bun5-hok, hian7-si5 hian3 i e5 si5-kan, ti7 chit e5 toe7-hng teh cho3 soan-to7 e5 kang-chok. Cha2-si5 toa3 ti7 Bu7-sia7 hiah-e5 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak--e5, tauh8-tauh8 chau2 loh8-lai5 piN5-iuN5, chng3-jip8 han3-jin5 e5 toe7-kai3, iah8 koaN7 chit8-koaN7 lang5-thau5-khak tng2-khi3. Chong2-si7 chiah-e5 cha2-si5 si7 ia2-ban5 lang5 e5 kiaN2-sun Bu7-sia7 tong5-paum chit-tiap8 loh8-lai5 piN5-iuN5, khiok m7-si7 ui7-tioh8 kau-chian3, si7 ui7-tioh8 beh choe3 le2-pai3, chiu7-si7 beh kap han3-jin5 saN-kap o-lo2 Siong7-te3, lai5 hoaN-hi2 ¡§Sin3 chit8-e5, Chu2 chit8-e5¡¨ e5 kau-poe5. 
